<h3 id="permittivity-function-of-an-artificial-dispersive-material">Permittivity Function of an Artificial Dispersive Material<a class="headerlink" href="https://meep.readthedocs.io/en/master/Python_Tutorials/Material_Dispersion/#permittivity-function-of-an-artificial-dispersive-material" title="Permanent link">#</a></h3>
<p>We will model a <em>uniform medium</em> of an artificial dispersive material. From the dispersion relation Žē(k), we will compute the numerical ╬Ą(Žē) via the formula:</p>
<p>
